name: "THE TINKER"- Gold Statue
description:
Statue of "Buckley Kristan" the Tinker on his exo-suit. This type of suit was known as an "fallout" suit back in the nuclear war back in 2200. Some areas of Earth 2.0 were contaminated with nuclear radiation and civilians are required to wear an exo-suit like this in public area. The Gold version of the suit were made for wealthy or important government aliens. This statue was made with a pure gold 100% with 1/1 scale of the real exo-suit. only 1 available in the metaverse 

*the winner of this bid will also get "Buckley Kristan" 1/1 ID
